The paper deals with image synthesis and learning, which are core topics in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed approach involves unsupervised learning, which is a common theme in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also deals with pose estimation and deformation, which are relevant to graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
